snippet.title: Note Ban: Long Queues for Cash Continue at Banks and ATMs

localized.description:
Note Ban: Long queues for cash continue at banks and ATMs. Peoples are standing in queues since mid-night to withdraw cash amid cash crunch after demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
